A vintage-style illustration depicting an intricate mechanical printing press transforming flowing streams of glowing XML code and angular brackets into crisp, elegant document pages emerging from the other side. The scene shows the transformation process as a cross-section view, with copper gears, brass tubes, and Victorian-era machinery aesthetic. Swirling data streams in deep blue and gold flow into the ornate contraption, while perfectly formatted paper sheets cascade out in a graceful arc. The background features a warm sepia-toned workshop atmosphere with subtle technical blueprints adorning weathered walls. Rich amber lighting illuminates the mechanical components, creating dramatic shadows and highlighting the intricate details of the data-to-document transformation process.
